    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Colorless-to-white crystalline potassium aluminum sulfate; has a wide range of uses, including in treatment of leather and textile, in sizing paper, as a mordant in dyeing, and as a water-purifying agent.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
